## Cloud/VM strain: no desktop environment, cloud-init for provisioning.
## This package list feeds the live-build ISO path AND is read directly by
## iso/cloud-image/build-cloud-image.sh, which builds this strain as a real
## qcow2 cloud image instead -- see iso/cloud-image/README.md.
cloud-init
## openssh-server lives here (and in server.list.chroot), NOT base.list.chroot:
## a cloud/VM instance needs sshd to be reachable at all, but the desktop strains
## never asked for an open :22. On the qcow2 path, build-cloud-image.sh already
## installs openssh-server explicitly, so there this line is a harmless idempotent
## re-install -- it's here so the live-build ISO path of this strain gets sshd too.
openssh-server
